        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Mindseed - Aundh"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "jharna kaul"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-20",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I & my husband fell in love with Mindseed, for our son, the day we visited the center for the first time! And during this 1.5 years, we never regretted our decision! The pedagogy, the concept & the execution is impeccable! The teachers(Ashwini teacher, Akshaya teacher, Shraddha teacher and all the didis), the support & ancillary staff and the Center Head (Angai ma'am) , everyone  has played a crucial role in our son's life! He calls it a Playcenter!!!\nMindseed is the place our children really need to be at. In today's uncertain & fast moving world, Mindseed gives our kids a lot of time & space to use their inherent potential so that our children flourish without being judged or compares!\nThank you Mindseed  for everything you are doing for our GenX! Wish you All the best! ☺☺💐💐",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Mindseed - Aundh"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "parvathi sethuraman"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-20",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Mindseed (Aundh, Pune) has very caring, practically efficient caretakers. I have dropped my twin boys from their 10th month and they are very happy and we even observe it in camera. The way the make them mingle with elderly kids in joyous sessions relevant to their age, timely they give our food per parents instruction, their open environment to play with multiple items is very reasonable. also they prep food and give as per schedule if parents would prefer that is included in fees. Timings, Fees, Location in Aundh, Pune suit working people and they ensure no excuses wrt food, medicines, care taking, timings. From principal, teachers, care takers all are very practical and so friendly.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
